If you are not seeing the screen below on your watch, then follow the steps listed below to put your watch into pairing mode: 1. Press the MENU button to access the main menu. Depending what state the watch is in you may need to press the MENU button more than once. 2. Use the up/down buttons to select "Settings" from the menu 3.
